Lord Year 2020, June 2nd, Tuesday, Italian Republic day
This is my Amiga version of a game supplied with Windows named MinedField.  
This game is freeware game for you, no source code at the moment, sorry!
However if you are interested of know which mode it has been made you should
search on Aminet the archive SteMarRegBlitzSources.lha that retains the source
code of the first uncompleted version of this game, plus some other sources for 
Blitz Basic 2.1 upward in plain text.
There is a known bug in the numbers displacement around the mines near edges,
sometimes it happens!
Now the game should show the exact zones map with different window borders!
Now there is my face as a present, so everybody should remember me!
Now the exit lock after the first play should never happen!
I am not responsible of any damage can occurs you using this game, you use it at
your own risk!
I wish you to enjoy with this game as me!

